Get "Configuration Backup to GitHub" up and running. https://home-assistant.io/docs/ecosystem/backup/backup_github/
  See also https://community.home-assistant.io/t/hassio-config-backup-strategy/28499/8
  Need working SSH https://home-assistant.io/addons/ssh/
  
Switch to local API in telldus. https://home-assistant.io/components/tellduslive/
  1) Delete tellduslive.conf
  2) Reboot Tellstick device
  3) Configure local API

Fix automation problem, light not turning off after five minutes?
 action:
  - data:
      entity_id: light.hallen_innanfor_dorren
    service: light.turn_on
  - delay: 'minutes: 5'
  - data:
      entity_id: light.hallen_innanfor_dorren
    service: light.turn_off
  alias: Hallway ligths on when arrive home
  condition: []
  id: '1515594690770'
  trigger:
  - entity_id: device_tracker.phone_phone
    event: enter
    platform: zone
    zone: zone.home

